item.title: Type Definition Model
item.description: A type_definition tree contains data type definitions that are not part of the primitive datatypes defined by HIM. The currently supported node types are suited for definition of structs. Node Types The node types for representing type definitions are: Branch Struct Property Please see more information about these node types here.
